FT  18 AUG 92 / World News in Brief: Woody Allen admits having an affair
Woody Allen, 56, admitted he was having an affair with Soon-Yi Previn, the
21-year-old adopted daughter of Mia Farrow, his partner for 12 years. The
film-maker is seeking custody of Satchel, his son by Farrow, and two
children they adopted.
